happy valentine’s day! my friend prompted this collab a few months ago and these are the dnp version of the three cheers for sweet revenge cover i made :) her part might be coming soon ;)) 

check out my friend’s instagram page here https://instagram.com/platonic.pml?utm_source=ig_profile_share&igshid=witdyrcg015q and stay tuned!
